# The Balance — an artfully crafted intellect

![essence of The Balance](the-balance.png)
<!-- carbon badge (8-bit portrait): the-balance.tiff -->

**what —** The law that Order and Chaos must balance.

**why —** Because the world cannot hold an excess of either, and survives only at equilibrium.

**how —** Every working of power exacts an equal cost; overreach burns the wielder to ash.

**where —** Everywhere, always — the true power of Recluce, beneath every mage on this roll.

*class: The Balance · the law that keeps the price · full weave in the-balance.spun · credit in the-balance.1099*

